Go!

45
00:07:33,320 --> 00:07:34,673
Don't cry.

46
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:39,519
Go!

47
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:45,675
Go, live and become!

48
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:48,638
