Tell him.

54
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:21,235
Okay.

55
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:29,473
A man doesn't cry.

56
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:05,153
When we get to the Holy Land,
we'll all be white,

57
