It's a land flowing
with milk and honey...

59
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:13,275
Paradise on Earth, my sweet.

60
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:36,234
Mommy.

61
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:31,038
Excuse me, my son,

62
00:12:31,920 --> 00:12:34,150
are there many albinos in Israel?

63
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:36,709
- You mean "whites"?
- Yes, whites.

64
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:40,790
In Israel, all Jews are white.

65
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:45,719
Aren't we in our country yet, my son?

66
00:12:45,920 --> 00:12:47,672
Haven't we reached Jerusalem?

67
00:12:48,040 --> 00:12:49,871
We have, father,

68
00:12:50,800 --> 00:12:55,078
we are in our country.
All of the country is Jerusalem!

69
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:58,590
Israel is the country
of our ancestors: Jerusalem!

70
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:19,989
No! No!

71
00:13:20,120 --> 00:13:21,712
What's wrong?

72
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:24,274
What's wrong?

73
