Calm down! Calm down!

74
00:13:29,160 --> 00:13:31,720
Israel has plenty of water!

75
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:36,588
There's enough water!
It's okay.

76
00:13:36,880 --> 00:13:40,589
Listen to me! It's okay!

77
00:13:41,800 --> 00:13:43,074
It's not my fault!

78
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:44,799
It's not my fault!

79
00:13:45,040 --> 00:13:47,156
It's not my fault!

80
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:51,348
Like this.

81
00:13:52,680 --> 00:13:53,749
Like this.

82
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:56,316
You see?

83
