269
00:32:16,960 --> 00:32:18,313
My present.

270
00:32:22,160 --> 00:32:24,833
If you want to write a diary,
I have one.

271
00:32:26,200 --> 00:32:28,634
This is good luck where I come from.

272
00:32:30,480 --> 00:32:33,074
A kippa, from us.

273
00:32:39,560 --> 00:32:41,073
- Hello!
- Hello, Mother.

274
00:32:41,560 --> 00:32:42,754
- Is he here?
- Yes.

275
00:32:42,880 --> 00:32:44,518
Did he get here by bus?

276
00:32:45,000 --> 00:32:46,399
No, we picked him up.

277
00:32:46,800 --> 00:32:48,279
Where is he?

278
00:32:48,960 --> 00:32:50,313
That's French.

279
00:32:50,440 --> 00:32:52,158
Our native language...

280
00:32:52,560 --> 00:32:55,632
Is this him?
He's so adorable!

281
00:32:56,160 --> 00:32:58,310
You take plane... no afraid?

282
00:32:59,240 --> 00:33:00,958
Mother, he speaks Hebrew.

283
00:33:01,160 --> 00:33:02,639
Hebrew in Ethiopia?

284
00:33:03,640 --> 00:33:06,393
