He's pale. I mean... pale-black.

285
00:33:06,480 --> 00:33:08,994
- He's fine, mother!
- Are you sure? Have you checked?

286
00:33:09,520 --> 00:33:11,795
Go see Dr. Cohen. He's wonderful.

287
00:33:11,920 --> 00:33:13,751
