He's doing fine!

288
00:33:19,080 --> 00:33:22,152
"Injara",
the traditional Ethiopian dish.

289
00:33:33,920 --> 00:33:35,035
Listen, Schlomo...

290
00:33:35,240 --> 00:33:37,037
I'd like to tell you that we know.

291
00:33:37,160 --> 00:33:39,230
Everything.

292
00:33:39,640 --> 00:33:41,517
We prefer to be clear...

293
00:33:42,760 --> 00:33:44,193
I wanted to tell...

294
00:33:44,320 --> 00:33:45,833
No, it's us...

295
00:33:46,040 --> 00:33:47,871
We're your parents now.

296
00:33:49,080 --> 00:33:51,958
Schlomo, we're left-wing people.

297
00:33:53,200 --> 00:33:55,555
- I wanted to tell...
- We like to be frank,

298
00:33:56,160 --> 00:33:58,594
honest, and respect others.

299
00:34:01,120 --> 00:34:02,997
So I'll be frank, Schlomo.

300
00:34:03,800 --> 00:34:05,074
We...

301
00:34:05,920 --> 00:34:07,433
we're not religious.

302
00:34:09,640 --> 00:34:12,234
We know that in Ethiopia, you were.

303
00:34:12,520 --> 00:34:14,988
You have always defended the Torah

304
00:34:15,520 --> 00:34:20,310
and survived because of your dreams
to return to Jerusalem.

305
00:34:21,240 --> 00:34:23,708
We respect that,
even if we're not practicing.

306
00:34:23,840 --> 00:34:25,831
If you'd like, tonight,

307
00:34:26,840 --> 00:34:29,070
we'll pray with you.

308
00:34:29,640 --> 00:34:31,631
We'll repeat after you.

309
00:34:50,520 --> 00:34:53,159
Thank you.
That's nice,

310
00:34:54,440 --> 00:35:00,436
