It's just that... not tonight.

311
00:35:03,920 --> 00:35:05,353
Let's sit down.

312
00:35:19,800 --> 00:35:22,439
Don't you like it?
Did she mess up?

313
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:25,913
Stomach ache.

314
00:35:26,120 --> 00:35:28,395
When I say that, it doesn't work!

315
00:35:28,560 --> 00:35:30,357
They make me finish my plate.

316
00:35:30,520 --> 00:35:32,590
Who do you like better,
Mickey or Donald?

317
00:35:32,800 --> 00:35:35,109
They don't have Mickey
in his country, dummy.

318
00:35:36,200 --> 00:35:38,668
What sport do you like, soccer?

319
00:35:40,600 --> 00:35:42,272
Walking.

320
00:35:51,480 --> 00:35:52,708
Good night.

321
00:35:54,560 --> 00:35:57,711
If you need anything,
come and wake me up.

322
00:36:00,680 --> 00:36:02,591
Mommy, come here! Mommy!

323
00:36:02,720 --> 00:36:03,948
Shut up!

324
00:36:37,080 --> 00:36:39,594
He's really big and muscly!

325
00:36:40,360 --> 00:36:42,271
He's handsome as a prince!

326
00:36:43,160 --> 00:36:44,798
Everyone.

327
00:36:45,120 --> 00:36:47,236
We have a new student:

328
00:36:47,600 --> 00:36:49,477
Schlomo Harrari.

329
00:36:50,960 --> 00:36:52,632
Take a seat, please.

330
00:36:58,880 --> 00:37:01,235
Let's carry on with the lesson,
